dcterms:description: The dataset contains nine features of tumors in 699 patients, with 241 malignant and 458 benign. The data are collected in different time periods, with a training set from January 1989 and a testing set from October 1989 to November 1991.
dcterms:title: Wisconsin Breast Cancer Dataset

dcterms:description: The MNIST dataset consists of 70,000 images of handwritten digits, with 60,000 images for training and 10,000 for testing. Each image is a 28x28 pixel grayscale image.
dcterms:title: MNIST Handwritten Digit Dataset
